<p>Using the following <a href={ "/assets/charade.html" }>content</a>, you will design and build an interface promoting the 1963 film "Charade". As the designer, feel free to make revisions to the structure of the content. The final deliverable will be a single HTML page but will appear to be the homepage of a microsite.</p>
