<ul>
  <li>Use <a href="https://getbootstrap.com">Bootstrap</a> or another framework</li>
  <li>Needs to be responsive (use <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/components/navbar/">Bootstrap's navbar</a>)</li>
  <li>Implements a <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/components/carousel/">carousel</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Any screen captures of the film are in the public domain, so consider using <a href="https://movie-screencaps.com/charade-1963/">screen caps</a> or searching on <a href="https://search.creativecommons.org/">Creative Commons Search</a>.</p>
